# Source files are UTF-8 (with BOM for .cs/.txt); the charset is enforced for
# editors via .editorconfig and for the compiler via Directory.Build.props
# (CodePage 65001). GitHub then renders the Russian text correctly. Line endings
# are left as-is here to keep encoding and EOL changes from being entangled.

# Bundled world/base data: preserve bytes exactly (no EOL conversion).
redist/** -text
